
Problem statement:
https://www.hackerrank.com/challenges/contest-leaderboard/problem


Solution
SELECT HACKER_ID, NAME, SUM(SCORE) AS SCORE1 FROM
(
SELECT A.HACKER_ID, NAME, CHALLENGE_ID, MAX(SCORE) AS SCORE
FROM SUBMISSIONS A LEFT JOIN HACKERS B ON (A.HACKER_ID = B.HACKER_ID)
GROUP BY A.HACKER_ID, NAME, CHALLENGE_ID
)A GROUP BY HACKER_ID, NAME
HAVING SUM(SCORE) > 0
ORDER BY SUM(SCORE) DESC ,A.HACKER_ID
